Interface AddressMapper

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddressMapperImpl
public interface AddressMapper

Address Mapper

MapStruct mapper for transforming address projections to domain models. Enriches Czech addresses with localized country, district, and municipality names. Handles both domestic (permanent/temporary) and foreign addresses.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček
